Waynesboro Va.  Jan. 23 1868

Mr. T.P. Jackson

Dear Sir
I wish to hire a good cook & worker for my family 5 persons.  For a good 
reliable woman I will give $6.00 Six Dollars per month the year round.  I 
prefer hiring 12 at a time everything is very convenient.  Water is 10 
steps of the kitchen & the wood always in the House.  The Labour is very 
light any Harty [sic] woman can do the work with ease & not employed 2/3 
